Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Clevo Control Center Maintainers <root@localhost>
Depends: libc6, zenity | kdialog
Recommends: pkexec, make, linux-headers-amd64
Provides: clevo-keyboard-led
Conflicts: clevo-keyboard-led
Replaces: clevo-keyboard-led
Description: Clevo/BlueSky control center for Linux
 Rust GUI, background service, and diagnostic CLI for Clevo/BlueSky laptops.
 The package includes the kernel module source and tries to build it for
 the running kernel during installation when headers are available.
